#: ../../../release/1.17.1-notes.rst:5
msgid "NumPy 1.17.1 Release Notes"
msgstr "NumPy 1.17.1 發行備註"

#: ../../../release/1.17.1-notes.rst:7
msgid ""
"This release contains a number of fixes for bugs reported against NumPy "
"1.17.0 along with a few documentation and build improvements.  The Python "
"versions supported are 3.5-3.7, note that Python 2.7 has been dropped.  "
"Python 3.8b3 should work with the released source packages, but there are no "
"future guarantees."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/1.17.1-notes.rst:13
msgid ""
"Downstream developers should use Cython >= 0.29.13 for Python 3.8 support "
"and OpenBLAS >= 3.7 to avoid problems on the Skylake architecture. The NumPy "
"wheels on PyPI are built from the OpenBLAS development branch in order to "
"avoid those problems."
msgstr ""

